snippet.title: Diana Shows Roma How to do Magic! Making a Magic Cauldron furry friend!
snippet.description:
This is an ad for Moose Toys’ Magic Mixies. Parents, your kids can experience the wonder of magic with the Magic Mixies Magic Cauldron. Watch their imagination come to life as they use their special Wand and magical ingredients to mix a potion that creates REAL Mist and a cute, fully interactive furry friend! Comes with over 50 sounds and reactions, and they can make magic happen again and again. Click here to pre-order while stocks last:
https://bit.ly/38hNLZp
Diana and Roma create a cute furry friend with the Magic Cauldron and magical ingredients!
Thanks for watching!
Subscribe to Kids Diana Show - http://bit.ly/2k7NrSx
